OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FShkreli ordered to repay   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F$64m                       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Martin Shkreli, the former drug firm   
OL,6, executive who ordered dramatic price   
OL,7, hikes of a life-saving medicine, has   
OL,8, been barred from the industry for life.
OL,10,FIn a decision on Friday, Judge Denise  
OL,11,FCote ordered him to repay $64.6m (#47m)
OL,12,Fin profits he made from the scheme.    
OL,14,FShe ruled that Mr Shkreli's actions had
OL,15,Fviolated laws against monopolies.      
OL,17,FMr Shkreli is currently serving a      
OL,18,Fprison sentence for defrauding         
OL,19,Finvestors.                             
